You can go there and buy a bus to drive there and sell. I did this in =
Italy=20
when I lived there. You can't bring it across the border and sell it =
here=20
if it is less than 25 years old.

They will make you sign some paperwork and possibly pay a deposit to =
bring=20
it across the border.

If you don't get it south of the border before a certain date you lose =
your=20
money and they come looking for you.

As I understand it - anything 25 years+ old can come across the border =
now.

